tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nWhere it says - \"save in\" you should click on the drop down box and save the file to your \"Desktop\" or another folder you can easily find.\r\n\r\nTo view MP4 file\'s you will need some kind of media player installed. Windows computers usually come with Windows Media Player already installed. Apple devices should have itunes installed.\r\n\r\nIf you haven\'t got a media player installed, you can download a free copy of <a href=\"http://uk.real.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Real Player</a> (also has a mac compatible version).','Instructions For Downloading Videos','','publish','closed','closed','','download-instructions','','','2015-10-17 22:41:52','2015-10-17 21:41:52','','0','http://igcsesciencecourses.com/membersarea/?page_id=300','0','page','','0');
